      <description>&lt;p&gt;I am currently a Research Fellow at Singapore University of Technology and Design, working with 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://sites.google.com/site/antoniosvarvitsiotis/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Antonios Varvitsiotis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
